  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "lotka-volterra",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lotka-volterra/yunxi/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.67,
      "size": 26784,
      "text": "一片森林里，住着一群兔子和一群狐狸。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lotka-volterra",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lotka-volterra/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.88,
      "size": 30096,
      "text": "兔子吃草繁衍，狐狸靠捕兔为生，谁也离不开谁。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lotka-volterra",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lotka-volterra/yunxi/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.09,
      "size": 33408,
      "text": "它们的数量会怎样此起彼伏？一个方程组给出了答案。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lotka-volterra",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "define-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lotka-volterra/yunxi/define-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32256,
      "text": "猎物方程：兔子按自然率增长，又按被捕食率减少。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lotka-volterra",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "define-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lotka-volterra/yunxi/define-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.17,
      "size": 34704,
      "text": "捕食者方程：狐狸靠吃到的兔子增多，又因自然死亡减少。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lotka-volterra",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "define-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lotka-volterra/yunxi/define-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.08,
      "size": 33264,
      "text": "两个变化率相互牵制，这就是洛特卡-沃尔泰拉方程组。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lotka-volterra",
      "section_id": "oscillate",
      "line_id": "osc-1",
      "filename": "oscillate-osc-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lotka-volterra/yunxi/oscillate-osc-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.58,
      "size": 25344,
      "text": "兔子一多，狐狸吃得饱，数量随之攀升。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lotka-volterra",
      "section_id": "oscillate",
      "line_id": "osc-2",
      "filename": "oscillate-osc-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lotka-volterra/yunxi/oscillate-osc-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.75,
      "size": 28080,
      "text": "狐狸一多，兔子被吃光，狐狸又开始挨饿减少。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lotka-volterra",
      "section_id": "oscillate",
      "line_id": "osc-3",
      "filename": "oscillate-osc-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lotka-volterra/yunxi/oscillate-osc-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.98,
      "size": 31680,
      "text": "两条曲线此消彼长，捕食者的高峰总是滞后于猎物。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lotka-volterra",
      "section_id": "phase",
      "line_id": "phase-1",
      "filename": "phase-phase-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lotka-volterra/yunxi/phase-phase-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.03,
      "size": 32544,
      "text": "把兔子数当横轴、狐狸数当纵轴，画出状态的轨迹。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lotka-volterra",
      "section_id": "phase",
      "line_id": "phase-2",
      "filename": "phase-phase-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lotka-volterra/yunxi/phase-phase-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.93,
      "size": 30816,
      "text": "轨迹是一条闭合的环，说明系统会周而复始地循环。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lotka-volterra",
      "section_id": "phase",
      "line_id": "phase-3",
      "filename": "phase-phase-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lotka-volterra/yunxi/phase-phase-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.33,
      "size": 37296,
      "text": "沿环运动时，一个守恒量始终保持不变，这是数学的秩序。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lotka-volterra",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lotka-volterra/yunxi/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.77,
      "size": 28368,
      "text": "调整初始兔子数量，看振荡的幅度如何改变。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lotka-volterra",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lotka-volterra/yunxi/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.95,
      "size": 31248,
      "text": "拖动被捕食率，感受狐狸的胃口如何左右整个周期。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lotka-volterra",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lotka-volterra/yunxi/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 31104,
      "text": "两个相互牵制的变化率，织出了生生不息的周期振荡。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lotka-volterra",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lotka-volterra/yunxi/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29376,
      "text": "相平面上的闭合环，正是这场循环最优雅的证明。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lotka-volterra",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lotka-volterra/yunxi/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.67,
      "size": 26784,
      "text": "简单方程写尽森林的兴衰，我们下次再见！"
    }
